org.jppf.node.protocol

Interface JobSLA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JobCommonSLA, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JPPFJobSLA

    public interface JobSLA
extends JobCommonSLA
    This interface represents the Service Level Agreement between a JPPF job and a server. It determines the state, conditions and order in which a job will be executed.
